e\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sun_Media\", \"score\": 0.9651081987446113, \"rank\": 0.032409333555069586, \"text\": \"Sun\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sun_Media\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sun_Media\"}, {\"begin\": 316, \"end\": 322, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jiajun\", \"score\": 0.8020135056823948, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jiajun\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jiajun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jiajun\"}, {\"begin\": 369, \"end\": 374, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999991778168, \"rank\": 8.221514097923328e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the four-man team\", \"from\": 277, \"to\": 294}, {\"ngram\": \"11 swimmers\", \"from\": 335, \"to\": 346}, {\"ngram\": \"a banned substance\", \"from\": 404, \"to\": 422}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They were allowed to swim because the China Anti-Doping Agency decided the positive tests were down to food contamination.\", \"from\": 425, \"to\": 547, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the China Anti-Doping Agency\", \"from\": 459, \"to\": 487}, {\"ngram\": \"the positive tests\", \"from\": 496, \"to\": 514}, {\"ngram\": \"food contamination\", \"from\": 528, \"to\": 546}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro.co.uk's live blog for updates from the Paris 2024 Olympics Peaty is certainly not entirely accepting of that judgement, suggesting that the athletes who tested positive should not be in Paris.\", \"from\": 549, \"to\": 755, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 607, \"end\": 620, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"2024 Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 749, \"end\": 754, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999991778168, \"rank\": 8.221514097923328e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Follow Metro.co.uk's live blog\", \"from\": 549, \"to\": 579}, {\"ngram\": \"updates\", \"from\": 584, \"to\": 591}, {\"ngram\": \"that judgement\", \"from\": 666, \"to\": 680}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 698, \"to\": 710}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'One of my favourite quotes in sport is that there is no point winning if you are not winning fair,' said Peaty said.\", \"from\": 757, \"to\": 874, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my favourite quotes\", \"from\": 765, \"to\": 784}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 788, \"to\": 793}, {\"ngram\": \"no point\", \"from\": 811, \"to\": 819}, {\"ngram\": \"Peaty\", \"from\": 863, \"to\": 868}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I think you know that in your heart.\", \"from\": 875, \"to\": 912, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your heart\", \"from\": 901, \"to\": 911}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you touch and you know you are cheating, then you are not really winning.\", \"from\": 913, \"to\": 989, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'So for me, if you have been \\\"contaminated\\\" twice, I think as an honourable person you should be out of the sport.\", \"from\": 991, \"to\": 1105, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an honourable person\", \"from\": 1053, \"to\": 1073}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 1095, \"to\": 1104}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But we know sport is not that simple.\", \"from\": 1106, \"to\": 1143, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 1118, \"to\": 1123}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'We have got to have faith in the system, but we do not.\", \"from\": 1145, \"to\": 1201, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"faith\", \"from\": 1166, \"to\": 1171}, {\"ngram\": \"the system\", \"from\": 1175, \"to\": 1185}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's just got to be stricter.\", \"from\": 1202, \"to\": 1231, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What I have said from the start is that it is fraud.\", \"from\": 1232, \"to\": 1284, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1263}, {\"ngram\": \"fraud\", \"from\": 1278, \"to\": 1283}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you are cheating, it is fraud.\", \"from\": 1285, \"to\": 1318, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fraud\", \"from\": 1312, \"to\": 1317}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's not about the podium.\", \"from\": 1320, \"to\": 1347, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 1336, \"to\": 1346}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We did our best job as a team, it may have been bronze, who knows, shoulda woulda coulda, who knows?\", \"from\": 1348, \"to\": 1448, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our best job\", \"from\": 1355, \"to\": 1367}, {\"ngram\": \"a team\", \"from\": 1371, \"to\": 1377}, {\"ngram\": \"bronze\", \"from\": 1396, \"to\": 1402}, {\"ngram\": \"shoulda woulda coulda\", \"from\": 1415, \"to\": 1436}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I am glad I was able to come out of my illness this week and give my best and be fair.\", \"from\": 1449, \"to\": 1539, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my illness\", \"from\": 1489, \"to\": 1499}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not need anything else to do that, just my heart, that's what sport is.\", \"from\": 1540, \"to\": 1616, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 1554, \"to\": 1562}, {\"ngram\": \"just my heart\", \"from\": 1580, \"to\": 1593}, {\"ngram\": \"what sport\", \"from\": 1602, \"to\": 1612}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And for me, being a man of faith, we can not take any of this with us, but we can take our pride and we can take the memories we share with our families, knowing we did it true.'\", \"from\": 1617, \"to\": 1795, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a man\", \"from\": 1635, \"to\": 1640}, {\"ngram\": \"faith\", \"from\": 1644, \"to\": 1649}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1684, \"to\": 1686}, {\"ngram\": \"our pride\", \"from\": 1704, \"to\": 1713}, {\"ngram\": \"the memories\", \"from\": 1730, \"to\": 1742}, {\"ngram\": \"our families\", \"from\": 1757, \"to\": 1769}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Peaty made it clear that he wasn't referring to the entire Chinese team, or other athletes, saying: 'I have also been asked about people who were not contaminated and I respect that.\", \"from\": 1797, \"to\": 1979, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1856, \"end\": 1863, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_people\", \"score\": 0.7665525176669575, \"rank\": 0.30045442928052135, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_people\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Peaty\", \"from\": 1797, \"to\": 1802}, {\"ngram\": \"other athletes\", \"from\": 1873, \"to\": 1887}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1927, \"to\": 1933}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not want to paint a whole nation or a group of people with one brush.\", \"from\": 1980, \"to\": 2054, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a whole nation\", \"from\": 2003, \"to\": 2017}, {\"ngram\": \"a group\", \"from\": 2021, \"to\": 2028}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2032, \"to\": 2038}, {\"ngram\": \"one brush\", \"from\": 2044, \"to\": 2053}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think that would be very unfair.'\", \"from\": 2055, \"to\": 2090, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 100m breaststroke silver medallist at this year's Gamesalso hit out at swimming chiefs, suggesting that they have not done their job properly.\", \"from\": 2092, \"to\": 2238, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 100m breaststroke silver medallist\", \"from\": 2092, \"to\": 2130}, {\"ngram\": \"this year's Gamesalso\", \"from\": 2134, \"to\": 2155}, {\"ngram\": \"swimming chiefs\", \"from\": 2167, \"to\": 2182}, {\"ngram\": \"their job\", \"from\": 2219, \"to\": 2228}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking of Team GB's performance going forward, he said: 'I think we are going to use it to our advantage in the next four years, whether I am there or not.\", \"from\": 2240, \"to\": 2397, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Team GB's performance\", \"from\": 2252, \"to\": 2273}, {\"ngram\": \"our advantage\", \"from\": 2333, \"to\": 2346}, {\"ngram\": \"the next four years\", \"from\": 2350, \"to\": 2369}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I know these boys will carry that and we will see how they do in four years' time.\", \"from\": 2398, \"to\": 2480, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these boys\", \"from\": 2405, \"to\": 2415}, {\"ngram\": \"four years' time\", \"from\": 2463, \"to\": 2479}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'But, the people that need to do their job, need to wake up and do it.'\", \"from\": 2482, \"to\": 2553, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the people\", \"from\": 2488, \"to\": 2498}, {\"ngram\": \"their job\", \"from\": 2515, \"to\": 2524}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Xu Jiayu and Pan Zhanle completed the Chinese team, with Xu saying: 'There is no problem for the team.\", \"from\": 2555, \"to\": 2657, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2555, \"end\": 2563, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xu_Jiayu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Xu Jiayu\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xu_Jiayu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xu_Jiayu\"}, {\"begin\": 2593, \"end\": 2600, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_people\", \"score\": 0.7665525176669575, \"rank\": 0.